{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775877173021,"sessionID":"ses_28579b10effeqzeeferpA1dQ0o","part":{"id":"prt_d7a87298a001EipvC32Q6qelLI","messageID":"msg_d7a87187d001QG06S2tMQqnpt3","sessionID":"ses_28579b10effeqzeeferpA1dQ0o","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_4561c189d6c1446a80ead5cc","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.github/tasks.md","limit":160},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.github/tasks.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-034: CI/CD GitHub Actions — Implementation Tasks\n2: \n3: **Module:** `.github`  \n4: **Language:** YAML  \n5: **Size:** L (12 workflows)  \n6: **Stage:** ST-3 completed → Implementation ready\n7: \n8: ---\n9: \n10: ## Phase 1: Core Workflows\n11: \n12: ### T001: main.yml — Docker build verification\n13: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n14: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n15: - [ ] Add `concurrency` group with cancel-in-progress\n16: - [ ] Add `docker/setup-buildx-action@v3`\n17: - [ ] Add `make docker-build` step\n18: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/main.yml`\n19: \n20: ### T002: lint.yml — Go lint with path filter\n21: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/lint.yml`\n22: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n23: - [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `lint` filter pattern\n24: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-go@v5` with Go 1.24\n25: - [ ] Add `make lint` step (conditional on path filter)\n26: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/lint.yml`\n27: \n28: ---\n29: \n30: ## Phase 2: Testing Workflows\n31: \n32: ### T003: test-coverage.yml — Go coverage with codecov\n33: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n34: - [ ] Configure `pull_request`, `merge_group`, `workflow_call` triggers\n35: - [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `coverage` filter (exclude `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`)\n36: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-go@v5` with Go 1.24\n37: - [ ] Add `go test` with coverage flags: `-race -v -coverprofile=coverage.out -coverpkg=./pkg/... ./pkg/...`\n38: - [ ] Add `codecov/codecov-action@v4` (conditional on `secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN`)\n39: - [ ] Add job output `coverage-passed` for `workflow_call` reuse\n40: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/test-coverage.yml`\n41: \n42: ### T004: e2e.yml — Kind cluster E2E tests\n43: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/e2e.yml`\n44: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n45: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-go@v5` with Go 1.23\n46: - [ ] Add `helm/kind-action@v1` with `install_only: true` (Kind v0.30.0)\n47: - [ ] Add `make e2e` step with env vars (`ARTIFACTS_PATH`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`, `ROUTER_URL`, `API_TOKEN`)\n48: - [ ] Add artifact upload on failure (`e2e-logs/`)\n49: - [ ] Add `always()` cleanup: `make e2e-clean`\n50: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/e2e.yml`\n51: \n52: ### T005: codegen-check.yml — Code generation verification\n53: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n54: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n55: - [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `codegen` filter pattern\n56: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-go@v5` with Go 1.24.4\n57: - [ ] Add `make gen-check` step (conditional on path filter)\n58: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/codegen-check.yml`\n59: \n60: ---\n61: \n62: ## Phase 3: Python Workflows\n63: \n64: ### T006: python-sdk-tests.yml — Python SDK unit tests\n65: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml`\n66: - [ ] Configure `pull_request`, `merge_group` triggers\n67: - [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `sdk` filter (`sdk-python/**`)\n68: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-python@v5` with Python 3.12\n69: - [ ] Add working directory `sdk-python`\n70: - [ ] Add pip install: `pytest`, then `pip install -e .`\n71: - [ ] Add `python -m pytest tests/ -v` step\n72: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/python-sdk-tests.yml`\n73: \n74: ### T007: python-lint.yml — Python Ruff linting\n75: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/python-lint.yml`\n76: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n77: - [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `python` filter pattern\n78: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-python@v5` with Python 3.10\n79: - [ ] Add `pip install ruff`\n80: - [ ] Add `ruff check . --config pyproject.toml` step (conditional on path filter)\n81: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/python-lint.yml`\n82: \n83: ---\n84: \n85: ## Phase 4: Quality Workflows\n86: \n87: ### T008: codespell.yml — Spelling verification\n88: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/codespell.yml`\n89: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n90: - [ ] Add backup/remove for `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json`\n91: - [ ] Add `pip install codespell`\n92: - [ ] Add `codespell` with `--check-filenames`, `--skip`, `--ignore-words-list`\n93: - [ ] Add restore step for backed-up files\n94: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/codespell.yml`\n95: \n96: ### T009: copyright-check.yml — Copyright header enforcement\n97: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/copyright-check.yml`\n98: - [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n99: - [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `copyright` filter (exclude `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**`)\n100: - [ ] Add `apt install moreutils` (for `ts` command)\n101: - [ ] Add `make gen-copyright` step\n102: - [ ] Add `git diff --exit-code` to verify no changes\n103: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml`\n104: \n105: ---\n106: \n107: ## Phase 5: Release Workflows\n108: \n109: ### T010: build-push-release.yml — Release image publishing\n110: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/build-push-release.yml`\n111: - [ ] Configure `push` trigger for `main` branch and tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*`\n112: - [ ] Add `actions/checkout@v3` (older version as per spec)\n113: - [ ] Add `actions/setup-go@v4` with Go 1.24.4\n114: - [ ] Add `docker/setup-buildx-action@v2`\n115: - [ ] Add `docker/login-action@v3` for GHCR (`ghcr.io`)\n116: - [ ] Set `TAG` from git ref and `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}`\n117: - [ ] Add `make docker-buildx-push` (workload manager)\n118: - [ ] Add `make docker-buildx-push-router`\n119: - [ ] Add `make docker-buildx-push-picod`\n120: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml`\n121: \n122: ### T011: dify-plugin-publish.yml — Dify plugin release automation\n123: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml`\n124: - [ ] Configure `push` trigger for tags `dify-plugin/v*`\n125: - [ ] Add download step for `dify-plugin` CLI 0.0.6\n126: - [ ] Add `yq` installation\n127: - [ ] Read and parse `manifest.yaml`\n128: - [ ] Package plugin to `.difypkg`\n129: - [ ] Checkout `author/dify-plugins` with `GH_TOKEN`\n130: - [ ] Move `.difypkg` to target repo\n131: - [ ] Branch, commit, push\n132: - [ ] Add `gh pr create` to `langgenius/dify-plugins`\n133: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml`\n134: \n135: ### T012: workflows-approve.yml — First-time contributor approval\n136: - [ ] Create `.github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml`\n137: - [ ] Configure `pull_request_target` with types `labeled`, `synchronize` for `main`, `release-**`\n138: - [ ] Add logic: detect first-time contributor vs `ok-to-test` label\n139: - [ ] Add `github-script` to list `action_required` workflow runs for SHA\n140: - [ ] Auto-approve if conditions met\n141: - [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/workflows-approve.yml`\n142: \n143: ---\n144: \n145: ## Phase 6: Integration & Validation\n146: \n147: ### T013: Workflow validation\n148: - [ ] Run `actionlint .github/workflows/*.yml` on all 12 workflows\n149: - [ ] Fix any syntax or configuration errors\n150: \n151: ### T014: Path filter verification\n152: - [ ] Create test file `pkg/test.go`, verify `lint.yml` triggers\n153: - [ ] Modify `sdk-python/file.py`, verify `python-lint.yml` and `python-sdk-tests.yml` trigger\n154: - [ ] Modify `README.md`, verify no Go/Python workflows trigger\n155: \n156: ### T015: Dry-run testing (optional)\n157: - [ ] Run `act -l` to list all workflows\n158: - [ ] Run `act -n` for dry-run (if `act` installed)\n159: \n160: ---\n\n(Showing lines 1-160 of 191. Use offset=161 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-034: CI/CD GitHub Actions — Implementation Tasks\n\n**Module:** `.github`  \n**Language:** YAML  \n**Size:** L (12 workflows)  \n**Stage:** ST-3 completed → Implementation ready\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Core Workflows\n\n### T001: main.yml — Docker build verification\n- [ ] Create `.github/workflows/main.yml`\n- [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n- [ ] Add `concurrency` group with cancel-in-progress\n- [ ] Add `docker/setup-buildx-action@v3`\n- [ ] Add `make docker-build` step\n- [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/main.yml`\n\n### T002: lint.yml — Go lint with path filter","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/.github/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775877173009,"end":1775877173019}}}}
