{"type":"text","timestamp":1775877246706,"sessionID":"ses_28579b10effeqzeeferpA1dQ0o","part":{"id":"prt_d7a883669001A16SYaNYBVoy7s","messageID":"msg_d7a88082c001jh6XAdv2Lx2N8p","sessionID":"ses_28579b10effeqzeeferpA1dQ0o","type":"text","text":"## Verification Summary for AR-034 — CI/CD GitHub Actions (12 workflows)\n\n**Status: Issues Found**\n\n### 12 Workflow Files Present ✅\n| Workflow | Purpose |\n|----------|---------|\n| main.yml | Docker build verification |\n| lint.yml | Go lint with path filter |\n| test-coverage.yml | Go coverage with codecov |\n| e2e.yml | Kind cluster E2E tests |\n| codegen-check.yml | Code generation verification |\n| python-sdk-tests.yml | Python SDK unit tests |\n| python-lint.yml | Python Ruff linting |\n| codespell.yml | Spelling verification |\n| copyright-check.yml | Copyright header enforcement |\n| build-push-release.yml | Release image publishing |\n| dify-plugin-publish.yml | Dify plugin release |\n| workflows-approve.yml | First-time contributor approval |\n\n### YAML Validation ✅\nAll 12 workflow files are valid YAML.\n\n### actionlint Issues Found\n\n| Issue | File | Severity | Notes |\n|-------|------|----------|-------|\n| Old action versions | build-push-release.yml | Warning | Per spec - intentional (v3 checkout, v2 buildx) |\n| Old action versions | Multiple workflows | Warning | dorny/paths-filter@v2 → v3 recommended |\n| `secrets` context in `if` | test-coverage.yml:69 | **Error** | `secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN` not available in workflow_call |\n| Path filter syntax | Multiple | Warning | False positive (YAML is valid) |\n\n### Main Issue: test-coverage.yml\nThe `if: steps.changes.outputs.coverage == 'true' && secrets.CODECOV_TOKEN != ''` condition at line 69 is problematic because:\n- When called via `workflow_call`, secrets are not directly accessible in `if` conditions\n- Should use `${{ inputs.CODECOV_TOKEN }}` when called as reusable workflow\n\n### Cannot Verify\n- Tests passing (requires GitHub Actions run history access)","time":{"start":1775877246705,"end":1775877246705}}}
